text: Aimee Lou Wood (born 3 February 1995) is a British actress. She is best known for her role as Aimee Gibbs in the Netflix original comedy-drama series Sex Education (2019â€“present). She also appeared in the films The Electrical Life of Louis Wain (2021) and Living (2022). Wood was born and raised in Stockport, Greater Manchester. She graduated from the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art (RADA) in 2017.
